VoltUI XLS Lite
================

This directory contains a deliberately reduced and hardened local fork used
only for read-only BIFF8 `.xls` spreadsheet extraction. It is derived from:

- github.com/extrame/xls at 4a6cf263071b975a90abf74ca3e804b48243be28
- github.com/extrame/ole2 at d69429661ad7efb189d2ad8074c867265009d0a4

Both upstream projects are licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
The full license is in LICENSE.

VoltUI modifications: removed the upstream process-terminating, stdout, and
debug logging paths; replaced unchecked OLE/BIFF reads with bounded error
returns; and retained only the compound-file and read-only cell extraction
needed by the Office MCP. This fork does not invoke Office, COM, Python, or
network services.
